<section class="our-story">
  <div class="our-story-inner">

    <div class="our-story-media">
      <img
        src="{{ 'br-hero-guasha-outdoor.webp' | asset_url }}"
        alt="BY RITUEL amethyst gua sha resting on warm linen"
        loading="lazy"
      >
    </div>

    <div class="our-story-body">
      <span class="section-label">Our Story</span>

      <h2 class="our-story-title">
        We built BY RITUEL for a very<br><span class="our-story-title-accent">specific morning.</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="our-story-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <p class="our-story-lede">
        Most skincare is <strong>passive</strong>. You apply something, you wait, you hope. We wanted something that actually <span class="our-story-accent">changed</span> how we looked in the mirror &mdash; the way the old rituals used to.
      </p>

      <p>
        So we took a practice that&rsquo;s been quietly working <strong>for generations across East Asia</strong>, and built the most beautiful version of it we could imagine. <strong>Hand-finished amethyst</strong>. Considered packaging. <strong>No shortcuts.</strong>
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Five minutes every morning.</strong> That&rsquo;s the whole promise. We wake up and do this ourselves &mdash; and that&rsquo;s the <strong>only testimonial that matters</strong> to us.
      </p>

      <p class="our-story-signature">&mdash; The BY RITUEL Team</p>

      <a href="{{ pages.about.url | default: '/pages/about-us' }}" class="our-story-link">
        Read the full story <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
      </a>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .our-story {
    background: var(--cream, #F7F2EA);
    padding: 120px 0;
  }
  .our-story-inner {
    max-width: 1320px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    padding: 0 40px;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .our-story-media {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--cream-dark, #EDE6D6);
    min-height: 640px;
  }
  .our-story-media img {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .our-story-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 72px 80px 72px 96px;
    background: var(--white, #FDFAF5);
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .our-story-body .section-label {
    font-family: var(--sans), system-ui, sans-serif;
    color: var(--terracotta, #B8704A);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 26px;
    display: block;
  }

  .our-story-title {
    font-family: var(--serif), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 54px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    color: var(--espresso, #1E120A);
    margin: 0 0 32px;
    max-width: 520px;
  }
  .our-story-title-accent {
    color: var(--terracotta, #B8704A);
  }

  .our-story-rule {
    width: 40px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--terracotta, #B8704A);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .our-story-lede {
    font-family: var(--serif), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(19px, 1.5vw, 22px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--espresso, #1E120A);
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    max-width: 520px;
  }
  .our-story-accent {
    color: var(--terracotta, #B8704A);
  }

  .our-story-body p:not(.our-story-lede):not(.our-story-signature) {
    font-family: var(--sans), system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #6E5A42;
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .our-story-signature {
    font-family: var(--serif), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: #A05E3C;
    margin: 18px 0 32px;
  }

  .our-story-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-family: var(--sans), system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--espresso, #1E120A);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding-bottom: 4px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--terracotta, #B8704A);
    align-self: flex-start;
    transition: color 0.25s ease;
  }
  .our-story-link:hover,
  .our-story-link:focus-visible {
    color: var(--terracotta, #B8704A);
  }
  .our-story-link:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--terracotta, #B8704A);
    outline-offset: 4px;
  }
  .our-story-link .arrow {
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--terracotta, #B8704A);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  .our-story-link:hover .arrow,
  .our-story-link:focus-visible .arrow {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .our-story {
      padding: 72px 0;
    }
    .our-story-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .our-story-media {
      min-height: 420px;
    }
    .our-story-body {
      padding: 56px 28px 64px;
      max-width: none;
    }
    .our-story-title {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .our-story-link,
    .our-story-link .arrow {
      transition: none;
    }
    .our-story-link:hover .arrow,
    .our-story-link:focus-visible .arrow {
      transform: none;
    }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Our Story",
  "presets": [{ "name": "Our Story" }]
}
{% endschema %}
